{
  "stem": "4189.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "See, we did not come on a, on a refugee visa from the HIAS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We came as individual immigrants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so we told the HIAS that we don't need any help, financial help.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "All we need is a job, that they should give us a job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, they said, OK, come back in a week or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we will see what we can do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So when we came back, he said-- they told us, look, we have a job for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But the job is in, in Providence, Rhode Island.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we will help you to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We will give you money, car fare to go there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We will give you money to rent a room in a rooming house and buy food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then once you, once you start to work and you earn money, you pay back the money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's how we will help you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there's one catch to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's the catch?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, since we did not bring you here, you did not come here on this, on this, on our visa, on our refugee visa, see, a displaced person visa-- yeah, this was-- President Truman at the time had passed legislation that he would take 100,000 displaced person to the United States, see?",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were here, were many of them here in New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the HIAS vouched for them that they would not be a burden to the state, see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But myself and my friend, we did not come under that displaced person act.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't fall under that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So therefore, they wanted us to bring them a paper from my uncle to state that he can no longer take care of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that then, then, therefore, they will vouch for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
